OL,3,CSo-called 'dine and dash' customers
OL,4,Cleave restaurant owner out of pocket
OL,6,FAn Italian restaurant owner from West
OL,7,FSussex who was left hundreds of pounds
OL,8,Fout of pocket because of so-called
OL,9,F"dine and dash" customers, has
OL,10,Fdescribed their actions as
OL,11,F"despicable".
OL,13,FPolice are investigating after a group
OL,14,Fof ten diners left the La Banca
OL,15,Frestaurant in Selsey without paying
OL,16,Ftheir #330 bill.
OL,18,FThe incident happened on August 31,
OL,19,Fwith restaurateur Neil Kimber saying
OL,20,Fit was distressing for staff, and had
OL,21,Fa huge effect on his business.
