OL,3,CSo-called 'dine and dash' customers
OL,4,Cleave restaurant owner out of pocket
OL,6,F"We served them all evening," he said,
OL,7,F"and checked back twice.
OL,9,F"They thought the food was absolutely
OL,10,Ffantastic. When they came to pay, they
OL,11,Fgot up, came out and said the food was
OL,12,Frubbish and they weren't going to pay
OL,13,Ffor it.
OL,15,F"And literally, just said here's #60
OL,16,Ffor the drinks and walked out with a
OL,17,F#395 bill...it's just despicable."
