OL,3,CSo-called 'dine and dash' customers
OL,4,Cleave restaurant owner out of pocket
OL,6,FHe says the group, which included
OL,7,Fwomen and six children, left staff
OL,8,Ffeeling intimidated, and that such
OL,9,Fbehaviour threatened the future of his
OL,10,Fbusiness.
OL,12,FCharging people up-front is an option
OL,13,Fbut not something he wants to do."We
OL,14,Fbelieve in honesty and trust, and
OL,15,Fthat's what we set our restaurant up.
OL,17,F"Honest food and trustworthiness. We
OL,18,Fhave a lot of local clientele and to
OL,19,Fstart charging them upfront, it just
OL,20,Fgoes against all our ethos.
