OL,3,CSo-called 'dine and dash' customers
OL,4,Cleave restaurant owner out of pocket
OL,6,F"But it does make us more vigilant and
OL,7,Fwe have to look at every single penny
OL,8,Fas do every sort of restaurant and pub
OL,9,Fthese days."
OL,11,FThe phenomenon isn't new but
OL,12,Fanecdotally, it's on the rise.
OL,14,FEarlier this summer, Anne and Bernard
OL,15,FMcDonagh, dubbed the "dine and dash
OL,16,Fcouple", were jailed for targeting
OL,17,Ffour restaurants in Wales at a cost of
OL,18,Fmore than #1100.
